               <p>I saw this waistcoat in Mr. Nicholls's shop on Thursday last, at nine in the morning; I afterwards saw the prisoner run down the street while I was having my hair dressed, and he dropped the waistcoat opposite the hair dresser's window, Mr. Nicholls's boy pursued the prisoner, and picked up the waistcoat, and gave it to his Master.</p>
